	<h2><a class="titles" href="./viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=15383">How to properly playback audio when creating an emulator</a></h2>


	<p class="moderators">Moderator: <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=group&amp;g=320">Moderators</a></p>

